## Auth Flow
- Supabase Auth with email magic link (MVP вЂ” phone OTP is Phase 2)
- Role passed in `user_metadata` during signup в†’ trigger creates profile row
- Middleware reads `profiles.role` and protects routes accordingly
- Login: email в†’ magic link в†’ redirect by role
- Register: choose role в†’ enter details в†’ magic link в†’ redirect

